cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the classification of Satellite Image Time Series (SITS) using deep learning approaches, specifically Temporal Convolutional Neural Networks (TempCNNs). This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of regularization mechanisms and hyper-parameter values, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the evaluation of the contribution of TempCNNs for SITS classification, which can be considered as an information retrieval (cs.IR) problem. Finally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which are a subset of neural networks (cs.NE).
